#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/stork-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Stork metrics are automatically enabled when the application also uses the xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[`quarkus-micrometer`] extension."
msgstr "As métricas do Stork são ativadas automaticamente quando o aplicativo também utiliza a extensão xref:telemetry-micrometer.adoc[quarkus-micrometer] ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/stork-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Micrometer collects the metrics of rest/grpc clients using Stork and the client using Stork programmatically."
msgstr "O Micrometer coleta as métricas dos clientes REST/gRPC que utilizam o Stork e do cliente que utiliza o Stork programaticamente."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/stork-reference.adoc
